<div class="alert alert-info mb-4" role="alert">
    <h4 class="alert-heading"><span class="bi bi-info-circle"></span> Keyed Navigation Sample</h4>
    <p>
        This page demonstrates MVVM navigation using <code>NavigateTo(key)</code> with string-based keys.
        The ViewModel is registered with a key using <code>ViewModelDefinition(Key = "...")</code> and the component 
        uses <code>[ViewModelKey]</code> attribute for resolution.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-gear"></span> Features Demonstrated</h6>
            <ul class="small">
                <li><strong>Key-Based Navigation:</strong> Navigate using string keys instead of types</li>
                <li><strong>ViewModelKey Attribute:</strong> Associates component with a specific ViewModel key</li>
                <li><strong>Multiple Implementations:</strong> Different ViewModels can implement same interface</li>
                <li><strong>Route Parameters:</strong> Supports relative paths and query strings</li>
                <li><strong>Flexible Resolution:</strong> Useful when ViewModel type is determined at runtime</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6><span class="bi bi-key"></span> Key vs Type Navigation</h6>
            <p class="small mb-2"><strong>Type-Safe:</strong> <code>NavigateTo&lt;TViewModel&gt;()</code></p>
            <ul class="small mb-2">
                <li>Compile-time safety</li>
                <li>Better refactoring support</li>
                <li>IDE IntelliSense</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="small mb-2"><strong>Keyed:</strong> <code>NavigateTo("key")</code></p>
            <ul class="small mb-0">
                <li>Runtime flexibility</li>
                <li>Dynamic ViewModel selection</li>
                <li>Plugin/module scenarios</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <p class="mb-0">
        <span class="bi bi-lightbulb"></span> <strong>Navigation Method:</strong>
        <code>MvvmNavigationManager.NavigateTo(nameof(TestKeyedNavigationViewModel), params)</code>
    </p>
</div>
